'''''Space Mutiny''''' (izwi nka  '''''Mutiny in Space)''''' ni film yasohotse muri 1988 muri [[Afurika]] y'Epfo ikorwa na American [[:en:Space_opera|space opera]] [[:en:Action_film|action film]] filimi yerekeye ubwato bwitwa ''Southern Sun''<ref>https://mst3k.fandom.com/wiki/Space_Mutiny_(film)</ref>''..'' Kuva ubwo iyi filime imaze guteza imbere umuco nyuma yo kugaragara mu gice kizwi cyane kuri televiziyo ''Mystery Science Theatre 3000'' <ref>https://www.radiotimes.com/movie-guide/b-zdl72s/space-mutiny/</ref>.

== Umugambi ==
''The Southern Sun'' ni ubwato bwibisekuruza, cyangwa ubwato bugenda mu kirere burimo abantu benshi<ref>https://www.rottentomatoes.com/m/space_mutiny</ref>, intego yabo ni ugukoloniza isi nshya. Urugendo rwabwo kuva kwisi yambere (bivuze ko ari [[Isi]] ) bumaze ibisekuruza cumi na bitatu<ref>https://www.themoviedb.org/movie/32148-space-mutiny</ref>, kuburyo benshi mubayituye bavutse kandi bazapfa batigeze bakandagiza ikirenge hasi<ref>https://www.themoviedb.org/movie/32148-space-mutiny</ref>. Ibi ntibishimisha abanzi, Eliya Kalgan ( John Phillip ), wafatanije naba pirate binjira muri sisitemu ya Corona Borealis yegeranye n’umuyobozi mukuru w’ubwato MacPhearson ( James Ryan )<ref>https://tvtropes.org/pmwiki/pmwiki.php/Film/SpaceMutiny</ref>. Kalgan yateguye umugambi wo guhungabanya uburyo bwo kugendesha ubwato bwa Southern Sun no gukoresha Enforcers<ref>https://en.battlestarwiki.org/Space_Mutiny</ref>, abapolisi b'ubwo bwato, kugira ngo bashimute ubwo bwato kandi babuyobore kuri ubu buryo. Kuri ubu, abatuye ''Southern Sun''' nta kundi byagenda uretse kwemera "ubuntu" bwe.<ref>https://awfulmovies.miraheze.org/wiki/Space_Mutiny</ref>

